    "description": "你是刺狼，一个像狼一样孤独的杀手，在遭到地藏组织的通缉后却成为被追杀的猎物。<br>你不甘失败，你在危机四伏的九夜世界中逃亡，不断获得新的战斗技能，激烈爽快地战斗，灵活巧妙地越过重重机关，强硬地对抗越来越凶狠诡异的敌人。你要探寻真相，生存下来，艰难地通往复仇之路。<br>   <br>面对不同种类的敌人，你需要有策略地进行战斗。  <br><br>腿击可以更加有效地破坏敌人的防具。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880200/extras/514465f19dbfaf8e997fbb614fe22b58.poster.avif?t=1690350761\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880200/extras/514465f19dbfaf8e997fbb614fe22b58.webm?t=1690350761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880200/extras/514465f19dbfaf8e997fbb614fe22b58.mp4?t=1690350761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>挑击可以更加有效地对付遁地敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880200/extras/6b6961619c2b5fbf1f046ae8ddb3940c.poster.avif?t=1690350761\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880200/extras/6b6961619c2b5fbf1f046ae8ddb3940c.webm?t=1690350761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880200/extras/6b6961619c2b5fbf1f046ae8ddb3940c.mp4?t=1690350761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>拥有适合自己的强大武力体系是杀手生存的保障，把你赚取的奖赏用来升级战斗招数，强化技能，或者购买武器和道具，以备在需要的时候使用。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880200/extras/7e95d97a447142296eb16653ec458b32.poster.avif?t=1690350761\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880200/extras/7e95d97a447142296eb16653ec458b32.webm?t=1690350761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880200/extras/7e95d97a447142296eb16653ec458b32.mp4?t=1690350761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br><br>跳跃攻击可以更加有效地打击高大的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880200/extras/bd350ea14690ef20ee7319a778e8e630.poster.avif?t=1690350761\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880200/extras/bd350ea14690ef20ee7319a778e8e630.webm?t=1690350761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880200/extras/bd350ea14690ef20ee7319a778e8e630.mp4?t=1690350761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>吸引敌人靠近以便使用绝学更有效地进行打击。  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880200/extras/6b2f5839779ad7d009ceb777ef9f9a16.poster.avif?t=1690350761\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880200/extras/6b2f5839779ad7d009ceb777ef9f9a16.webm?t=1690350761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880200/extras/6b2f5839779ad7d009ceb777ef9f9a16.mp4?t=1690350761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>更多可能的组合出招等待您的创造性发挥。",
